data.description: Country peaceful living with beautiful views is what this home offers. A beautifully designed manufactured home on a foundation that offers lots of natural light with an open floor plan and abundance of windows. New roof, new exterior & interior paint and new flooring. A wood burning fireplace and a wood stove will keep you warm on the coming winter nights. The kitchen offers a stainless steel fridge, painted cabinets and a pantry. The office has a view and French doors.  The property has a lean-to, tack room area, hay barn, wood lean-to that need some work but could be restored. There is room to build a shop, room for RV parking, room to build your own garden too. Plus a storage shed for all your extra stuff. A fenced pasture awaits your animals.  There are decks on the front and back for those lazy days.
